  "title": "IMMEDIATE [ Office Hours ] Locum Staff Nurse Renal Dialysis 29/hr #HYT",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Title:</strong> Agency Staff Nurse (Renal Dialysis)<br /> <strong>Location:</strong> Novena (Govt)<br /> <strong>Employment Type:</strong> Contract / Agency (Immediate Start)<br /> <strong>Pay Rate:</strong> $29 per hour<br /> <strong>Working Hours:</strong> Monday – Friday, 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM<br /> <strong>Available Positions:</strong> 3</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Provide professional nursing care and dialysis treatment to renal patients.</li><li>Prepare, operate, and maintain dialysis machines and equipment.</li><li>Monitor and record patients’ vital signs before, during and after treatment.</li><li>Administer prescribed medications and perform blood taking when required.</li><li>Assist doctors during procedures and respond to medical emergencies.</li><li>Educate patients on dialysis and post-treatment care.</li><li>Ensure infection control and accurate documentation at all times.</li><li>Support daily operations of the dialysis unit through team collaboration.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Valid SNB registration and current BCLS certification.</li><li>Dialysis trained and proficient with hemodialysis equipment.</li><li>Minimum 1 year of relevant nursing experience preferred.</li></ul><p>All qualified applicants, please<strong> click “ APPLY NOW”</strong></p><p>Or you may send in your resume to:</p><p><strong>Whatsapp: </strong><u><strong>https://wa.me/+6597430026</strong></u></p><p><strong>Email : </strong><a href=\"mailto:kimlow@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><u><strong>kimlow@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></u></a></p><p>Kimmy Low Yi Ting (Kim) | CEI Registration Number: R23112122</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd Company Reg. No. 199601303W | EA LICENCE Number: 99C4599</p>",
